name: Seedbox
body:
SeedboxManager
==============

SeedboxManager is an automated task manager for synchronizing files from a seedbox to your home library.

**Current status:**

[![Build status](https://travis-ci.org/shad7/seedbox.png?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.org/shad7/seedbox) [![Coverage](https://coveralls.io/repos/shad7/seedbox/badge.png)](https://coveralls.io/r/shad7/seedbox) [![Version](https://badge.fury.io/py/SeedboxManager.svg)](http://badge.fury.io/py/SeedboxManager) [![Requirements Status](https://requires.io/github/shad7/seedbox/requirements.png?branch=master)](https://requires.io/github/shad7/seedbox/requirements/?branch=master)
